# wp.org-shape ZIP exclude list. Must stay in sync with `release.md::COMMON_EXCLUDES`
# plus the wp.org-only excludes (run-scan.php, cp-api-fetch-polyfill.js).
# See release.md for the dual-ZIP build flow.

# VCS / dotfiles
